Definition: the communication of an attitude or emotional state among a number of people
Example: a contagion of mirth; the infection of his enthusiasm for poetry
Synonyms: adj, all, infectious, contagious, infection, verb, cognition, infect, noun, Tops, communication, the, of, an, attitude, or, emotional, state, among, a, number, people, mirth, his, enthusiasm, for, poetry
Category: noun.communication
